$interpreted: Juan-Yun: They've been in there for a while. I wonder if they've completed the trial yet...
Juan-Yun: Isn't that the Tapir Chieftain!? What's going on!?
Panicked Person: Yaagh! It's a killer, run!!
Shun: Traitor! I will avenge General Yu!
Yao: Got a death wish!? Consider it granted!
Pang: Quick, get General Shun out of here.
Yao: You're a pain in the ass!
Maeok: Get everyone out of here!
Qing-Feng: Arbiter, we'll help evacuate the people. You take care of the traitor!
Turtle Chieftain: Yeah, clean up the mess you made!
Maeok: Toyokuni, protect the Tapir Chieftain. I will help Pang.
Maeok: Pang! Let's do this together, don't go easy on him!
Juan-Yun: They're here, but what about Tindoiimu?
Himawari: Quit worrying about her, Juan-Yun! Let's just get out of here!
Maeok: You're no match for us alone, Yao!
Maeok: Pang, do it! I have him pinned down!
Yao: What, you still see me as a friend? Hah! I thought you wanted justice more than friendship! So just kill me already!!
Yao: Kill me and bury your guilt!
Yao: Make a decision or get out of here!
Pang: No... I've made up my mind... I don't want any more regret...
Pang: I... I know... I know what I must do!!
Yao: It's all up to you, now!
Frantic Person: Oh no, the arbiter's been defeated, too!? How!?
Scared Person: We're all gonna die!!
Puggi: Waaagh! That crazy tiger's coming to kill us!
Yao: You Komainu are tough, I'll give you that, but---
Toyokuni: (How in the... Does he not feel any pain?)
Pang: ...Hagh... gah... I have to... save everybody...
Pang: Ah... gah... gyahh! Dieee! Dieeeee!!
Jia-Shen: Pang, buddy, what in tarnation are ya doin'!? Stop that!
Puggi: Pang? B-Big bro!? Wake up!!
Yao: Gah... hagh... This is the end... Pang...
Puggi: Pang, wake up! Something bad's happening!!
Scared Person: Oh no, we're really all going to die here!!
Scared Person: Oh, it's Chiyuki's voice!
Chiyuki: Everyone, come to my voice! It's safe here!
Chiyuki: Puggi, take Pang to safety!
Chiyuki: I'm the host! It's my job to assure the safety of my audience!
Jia-Shen: ...Alright, well. Take care of yerself!
Chiyuki: Don't worry, chieftain! I'm coming!
Chiyuki: ...You don't remember me? You saved me once...
Yao: Of course I don't remember. You're of no importance.
Chiyuki: P-Please don't hurt anyone. I know you're not a bad person, I could tell that when you saved me...
Yao: ...What a joke. You see me once before and suddenly you know me?
Yao: Forget it. You're a victim of this crooked Alliance just the same. Move out of my way, and I'll let you live.
Chiyuki: N-No! Even if it is you, my savior, I can't let you pass!
Yao: Are you not afraid to die?
Chiyuki: I-I'll fight just as hard as you, if it means protecting my audience!
Yao: You'll die for people you don't know? Is that really worth it?
Chiyuki: Of course it's worth it. They're my fans.
Yao: Alright, you brought this on yourself though.
Yao: Sorry, I had to do what I had to do.
